Mullaly Park: A view eastward across the section of the park which is located between East 165th (left) and East 164th Streeta. Also shown is the elevated structure of the Woodlawn subway line on River Ave. The vantage-point is the Park Plaza Building on the west side of Jerome
Ave.
1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Writers' Project photo.
